          "guid": "mrx0v028pwyh35xj",
          "message": {
            "text": "Verified frame-by-frame by loading the captured SVG in Chromium and screenshotting at computed frame times (frame windows extracted from the emitted `fv-N` keyframe percentages): per-line typing with caret renders mid-word; the editorвҶ’terminal and terminalвҶ’browser glides show genuine mid-flight window scaling; the terminal link click shows the macOS hand cursor; the selection frame highlights `\\\"btn\\\"` in blue before `{cls}` lands; the hot-at-5 frame shows the orange button matching the on-screen code exactly (label always 'Clicked N times' вҖ” no pluralization the code doesn't have); the end card renders a clean wordmark with the cursor parked in deliberate empty space. 31 frames, 756 KB raw / ~95 KB gzipped.",
            "markdown": "Verified frame-by-frame by loading the captured SVG in Chromium and screenshotting at computed frame times (frame windows extracted from the emitted `fv-N` keyframe percentages): per-line typing with caret renders mid-word; the editorвҶ’terminal and terminalвҶ’browser glides show genuine mid-flight window scaling; the terminal link click shows the macOS hand cursor; the selection frame highlights `\\\"btn\\\"` in blue before `{cls}` lands; the hot-at-5 frame shows the orange button matching the on-screen code exactly (label always 'Clicked N times' вҖ” no pluralization the code doesn't have); the end card renders a clean wordmark with the cursor parked in deliberate empty space. 31 frames, 756 KB raw / ~95 KB gzipped."
          },
